Package it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group.content

Class Link

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group.content.Link
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Request, Group, java.io.Serializable
    public final class Link
extends java.lang.Object
implements Group
    The Link class defines a task request, sent from an actor space service provider, for asking a remote actor space service provider to add the reference associated with the local group to the references of the remote group. Note that the operation is performed only if the requester is an actor space provider. There is not an answer for such a kind of request.
